/* Intentionally empty.
 *
 * GTK loads this file at GTK_STYLE_PROVIDER_PRIORITY_USER — the highest
 * priority, which overrides ANY application stylesheet regardless of
 * selector specificity. eww loads its own CSS at APPLICATION priority, so
 * every rule written here leaks into eww widgets (rounded light backgrounds
 * on bar buttons and wifi list rows, etc.) and cannot be overridden from
 * eww's SCSS.
 *
 * The glassmorphism styles live in the catppuccin-glass theme instead:
 * ~/.themes/catppuccin-glass/gtk-3.0/gtk.css (managed by chezmoi under
 * dot_themes/). Themes load at THEME priority, below eww's APPLICATION,
 * so eww keeps full control of its own styling.
 */
